query:
INSERT INTO maintenanceRecords (vehicleId, maintenanceType, description, cost, performedAt, mileageAtService, kmDueMaintenance) 
SELECT id, 'Oil Change', 'Regular oil change service', 50.00, NOW(), 10000, 15000 
FROM vehicles 
WHERE plateNumber = 'M 412458' 
LIMIT 1;
